member.example:
This sample shows how to display the avaliable scanner sources window.

           imgScan.SelectSource()

           imgScan.SelectSource();

This sample shows how to display the avaliable scanner sources window.

           Dim Result as Boolean = imgScan.SelectSource(Me)

           Boolean Result = imgScan.SelectSource(this);

This sample shows how to checks if the specified source is active.

           Dim IsActive As Boolean = imgScan.IsSourceActive("MyScannerName")

           Boolean IsActive = imgScan.IsSourceActive("MyScannerName");

This sample shows how get all the active sources on the system.

           Dim Sources As ArrayList = imgScan.GetScannerSources()

           ArrayList Sources = imgScan.GetScannerSources();

This sample shows how start acquiring images from the selected scanner.

           imgScan.SaveImageFormat = ImageComponents.ImgScan.OutputFormat.TIF
           imgScan.SaveImageCompression = ImageComponents.ImgScan.Compression.CCITT4
           imgScan.ImageFileDirectory = "C:\Test\"
           imgScan.Acquire()

           imgScan.SaveImageFormat = ImageComponents.ImgScan.OutputFormat.TIF;
           imgScan.SaveImageCompression = ImageComponents.ImgScan.Compression.CCITT4;
           imgScan.ImageFileDirectory = "C:\\Test\\";
           imgScan.Acquire();
